You don't need a linklib for egcs. It uses assembler inlines for Warp3D
function calls. Somewhere in your code you must include Warp3D/Warp3D_protos.h
to get them defined. Maybe you have an old version (the one in the Warp3D
archive is only for Warp3D V1, so it misses the new V2 functions). I can mail
you an uptodate version if you want.
 
